sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>Watch Stream
    participant UserNS as User Namespace
    participant IstioCP as Istio Control Plane
    participant Authorino as Authorino Service
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus Operator

    %% Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (KServe Serverless)
    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: InferenceService Reconciliation (KServe Serverless Mode)
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: User Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>TLS1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Get InferenceService Details<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>UserNS: Create OpenShift Route<br/>API Call TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>UserNS: Create Istio VirtualService<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>UserNS: Create Authorino AuthConfig<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>UserNS: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>UserNS: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>UserNS: Create Telemetry<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>UserNS: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>UserNS: Create PodMonitor<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>UserNS: Create RoleBinding for Prometheus<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>IstioCP: Update ServiceMeshMemberRoll<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
    end

    %% Flow 2: StorageSecret Reconciliation
    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: StorageSecret Reconciliation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create Data Connection Secret<br/>Label: opendatahub.io/managed=true<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: User Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event (Secret)<br/>TLS1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List All Labeled Secrets in Namespace<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>UserNS: Create/Update storage-config Secret<br/>Aggregated S3 credentials<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
    end

    %% Flow 3: Custom CA Certificate Propagation
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Custom CA Certificate Propagation
        note over K8sAPI: OpenShift CA Operator injects<br/>cluster CA bundle into<br/>odh-trusted-ca-bundle ConfigMap
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event (ConfigMap)<br/>TLS1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Get CA Bundle from ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>UserNS: Create/Update odh-kserve-custom-ca-bundle<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        Controller->>UserNS: Update storage-config Secret<br/>Add certificate field<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
    end

    %% Flow 4: Knative Service Validation (Webhook)
    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: Knative Service Validation (Webhook)
        note over K8sAPI: KServe Controller creates<br/>Knative Service for InferenceService
        K8sAPI->>Controller: POST /validate-serving-knative-dev-v1-service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS (Service CA)<br/>Auth: K8s API Server mTLS
        Controller->>Controller: Validate Knative Service Configuration
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Return AdmissionReview Response<br/>mTLS
        note over K8sAPI: API Server allows/denies<br/>Knative Service creation
    end

    %% Flow 5: Monitoring RoleBinding Creation
    rect rgb(255, 255, 220)
        note over User,Prometheus: Flow 5: Monitoring RoleBinding Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: User Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>TLS1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>UserNS: Create RoleBinding<br/>Grant prometheus-custom SA<br/>Access to prometheus-ns-access ClusterRole<br/>API Call TLS1.2+
        note over Prometheus: Prometheus can now scrape<br/>metrics from namespace
    end
